GRC Roadmap (Zero to Hero)
│
├── 1. Fundamentals of Governance, Risk, and Compliance
│   ├── Understanding Governance
│   │   └── Setting up Organizational Security Policies
│   ├── Risk Management
│   │   └── Risk Identification, Analysis, Mitigation
│   ├── Compliance Frameworks
│   │   └── PCI DSS, HIPAA, GDPR, ISO 27001
│   └── Legal, Regulatory, and Industry Standards
│
├── 2. Information Security Management Systems (ISMS)
│   ├── ISO 27001
│   │   ├── ISMS Documentation
│   │   ├── Risk Assessment and Treatment
│   │   └── Internal Audit
│   └── NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF)
│
├── 3. Risk Management Frameworks
│   ├── NIST 800-53 (Risk Management Framework)
│   ├── COBIT (Control Objectives for IT)
│   ├── FAIR (Factor Analysis of Information Risk)
│   └── COSO (Committee of Sponsoring Organizations)
│
├── 4. Compliance Auditing
│   ├── PCI DSS (Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard)
│   ├── HIPAA (Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act)
│   ├── SOC 2 (System and Organization Controls)
│   └── GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation)
│
├── 5. Risk Assessment and Analysis
│   ├── Risk Register
│   ├── Threat Modeling
│   ├── Risk Treatment Plans
│   └── Risk Appetite and Tolerance
│
├── 6. Internal Auditing and Monitoring
│   ├── Audit Logs and Monitoring
│   ├── SIEM Integration
│   └── Evidence Collection for Audits
│
├── 7. Third-Party Risk Management
│   ├── Vendor Risk Assessments
│   ├── Contractual Compliance
│   ├── Continuous Monitoring of Vendor Compliance
│   └── Due Diligence for Third-Party Providers
│
├── 8. Incident Response and Business Continuity
│   ├── Incident Response Plan (IRP)
│   ├── Business Continuity Planning (BCP)
│   ├── Disaster Recovery Planning (DRP)
│   └── Crisis Management
│
├── 9. Data Privacy and Protection
│   ├── GDPR, CCPA Compliance
│   ├── Data Protection Impact Assessments (DPIA)
│   ├── Data Retention Policies
│   └── Data Encryption and Anonymization
│
└── 10. Soft Skills and Communication
    ├── Policy Writing and Documentation
    ├── Communicating with Stakeholders
    └── Reporting Risk and Compliance Metrics
